  "title": "Nautilus Shell - Stardew Valley Wiki",
  "description": "The Nautilus Shell is found via foraging at The Beach in Winter. The player may randomly receive one in the mail from Demetrius. It can also be received as a gift at the Feast of the Winter Star. It may also spawn on the Beach Farm during any season. It may also be found foraging on levels 1-29 of the Mines while the Shrine of Challenge is enabled, or the Danger in The Deep quest is active. It can also be gifted by a pet turtle with max friendship, or randomly found at the Traveling Cart for data-sort-value=\"120\"360–1,000g. One Nautilus Shell can be purchased from Demetrius' shop at the Desert Festival for data-sort-value=\"50\"> 50 Calico Eggs.",
